config BR2_PACKAGE_WINE_MONO
	bool "wine-mono"
  depends on BR2_i386 || BR2_x86_64
  help
    Wine Mono is a package containing Framework Mono and other projects,
    intended as a replacement for the .NET Framework (4.8.1 and earlier) in Wine.
    It works in conjunction with Wine's builtin mscoree.dll,
    and it is not intended to be useful for any other purpose.

    https://github.com/wine-mono/wine-mono
